cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with conversational modeling. The use of neural networks and deep learning techniques in the proposed model suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper's focus on generating diverse and interesting responses indicates that it could also be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
